==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mailable
<hw>Mail"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Admissible lawfully
into the mail. Opposed to <ant>non-mailable</ant>. Dangerous items such
as explosives, weapons, or corrosive chemicals are often classified by
the postal authorities as non-mailable.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

